<view class="page-shell"><view class="custom-nav" style="padding-top: {{navTop}}px; height: {{navHeight}}px;"><view class="back-button" bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}" mode="aspectFit" /></view><view class="nav-copy"><view><text>更正记录详情</text><text>M45</text></view><text>查看更正记录的完整信息、处理过程及影响范围</text></view></view><scroll-view class="page-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height: {{navSpacer}}px;"></view><view class="content">
  <view class="record-hero"><view class="record-symbol">▤</view><view class="record-id"><text>更正记录编号</text><text>CR20250513001</text><text>● 已审批</text></view><view class="record-meta"><view><text>更正类型</text><text>课时误记更正</text><text>审批时间</text><text>2025-05-13 15:05</text></view><view><text>提交时间</text><text>2025-05-13 14:32</text><text>当前状态</text><text>已完成（账务已更新）</text></view></view></view>
  <view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">申请人与审批人</view><view class="people-grid"><view><text>申请人（校区管理员）</text><view>👤<text>李明</text></view><text>南湖校区</text></view><view><text>审批人（总部管理员）</text><view>👤<text>王强</text></view><text>总部运营部</text></view></view></view>
  <view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">处理流程时间线</view><view class="timeline-row" wx:for="{{timeline}}" wx:key="title"><view class="timeline-mark">✓</view><view><text>{{item.title}}</text><text>{{item.detail}}</text></view><text>{{item.time}}</text></view></view>
  <view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">更正内容对比</view><view class="compare-table"><view class="table-head"><text>项目</text><text>更正前（错误记录）</text><text>→</text><text>更正后（正确记录）</text></view><view class="table-row" wx:for="{{comparisons}}" wx:key="label"><text>{{item.label}}</text><text>{{item.before}}</text><text>→</text><text>{{item.after}}</text></view></view></view>
  <view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">影响范围</view><view class="impact-grid"><view><text>▤　课时余额影响</text><view><text>更正前余额</text><text>12 课时</text></view><view><text>更正后余额</text><text>13 课时</text></view><view><text>变化</text><text>+1 课时</text></view></view><view><text>▣　财务账目影响</text><view><text>更正前金额</text><text>-￥240.00</text></view><view><text>更正后金额</text><text>-￥120.00</text></view><view><text>变化</text><text>+￥120.00</text></view></view></view></view>
  <view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">关联证据　<text>共 2 个附件</text></view><view class="attachment-grid"><view><image src="{{courtPhoto}}" mode="aspectFill" /><view><text>学员沟通记录.jpg</text><text>2025-05-13 14:30 · 1.2MB</text></view></view><view><image src="{{courtPhoto}}" mode="aspectFill" /><view><text>课程签到表.jpg</text><text>2025-05-13 14:31 · 1.5MB</text></view></view></view></view>
  <view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">审计轨迹</view><view class="audit-table"><view class="audit-head"><text>操作时间</text><text>操作人</text><text>操作角色</text><text>操作内容</text></view><view class="audit-row" wx:for="{{audits}}" wx:key="time"><text>{{item.time}}</text><text>{{item.operator}}</text><text>{{item.role}}</text><text>{{item.action}}</text></view></view><view class="audit-note"><text>说明</text><text>本更正记录已审批通过且账务已更新，无法直接回滚。如需调整，请重新发起更正申请并说明原因。</text></view></view>
  <view class="bottom-actions"><button bindtap="openAnomaly">↗ 查看关联异常</button><button bindtap="exportRecord"><image src="{{icons.download}}" mode="aspectFit" />导出记录</button></view><view class="safe-space"></view>
</view></scroll-view></view>
